title: Natural Born Sellers
overview: Natural Born Sellers follows real estate agents and identical twins Julianna and Marissa Stoap, and their parents Rick and Glorie Lee Beyenhof, who are all unlike any agents you know. The hot young twins were raised on real estate as they watched their parents powerhouse partnership rise to the top. Now the twins follow in their footsteps, becoming an unbeatable team themselves. Their signature all-in-the family style, with equal parts passion, quirky fun, and fearless negotiation skills, makes them some of California's most sought-after and successful agents.
